[3] Saudi Arabia: 0 new cases, 0 new deaths - MOH 24 Jun 2015
Date: Wed 24 Jun 2015
Source: Saudi Arabia MOH 24 Jun 2015 [edited]
http://www.moh.gov.sa/en/CCC/PressReleases/Pages/Statistics-2015-06-24-001.aspx


As of 12 Noon today, 24 Jun 2015, there have been a total of:
1038 laboratory confirmed cases of MERS-CoV infection including
460 deaths,
575 recoveries and
3 currently active cases

During the past 24 hours there have been a total of:
0 newly confirmed cases
0 newly reported fatalities and
1 newly reported recovery

[The reported case fatality rate is 44.3 percent]

Information on newly reported recovery:
A 52-year-old male, non healthcare worker from Hufoof, with a history of pre-existing co-morbidities. [was reported as a confirmed case on 19 Jun 2015 at which time he was noted to be in stable condition. - Mod.MPP]

